{"tid":1894997,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"放屁或會傳染武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-02-24T09:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T09:48:25.000Z","uid":154406,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1cafcc006e39206589f92f37589444d3cae3e2","tid":1894997,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"先前中國大陸抗 SARS 專家鐘南山曾在 COVID-19 （武漢肺炎）患者的糞便中分離出病毒，造成網友一片憂心，認為武漢肺炎有糞口傳染的可能性，甚至關心「放屁」的舉動是否有傳染疑慮？就有專家引用國外研究數據，認為如果真的要達到「放屁傳染」，需要滿足 2 個條件。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸江蘇疾病控制中心公眾號引用澳洲科普專家卡爾&middot;克魯斯澤爾尼克（ Karl Kruszelnicki ）與微生物學家路克&middot;坦能（ Luke Tennent ）的一份研究，分別有無穿著褲子，在 5 公分的距離下對培養皿放屁。<br />\n<br />\n隔天觀察結果，只有脫褲子放屁的培養皿有長出只存活於腸道內或皮膚表面的細菌，且其菌種為無害的，穿褲子放屁則沒有引起細菌增長，代表衣物存在過濾的效果。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇疾控中心總結，雖然以上為針對細菌而非病毒的實驗，不過可作為參考，而且實驗者離培養皿距離非常近，相信也不會有人距離這麼近吸入，因此若真的放屁傳染，需先滿足 2 個前提條件，「脫褲子猛放屁」、「內褲換洗習慣不佳」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20200224/3952860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20200224%2F3952860&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=951eb08d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20200224/3952860</a><br />\n<br />\n蓋清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d95d38e4caeed0389d57b7fbcdda2f88b65277b","tid":1894997,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"放濕屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad5d5ae6f482d16ef030c3194c9b9ca8bd296a4","tid":1894997,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:45:28.000Z","msg":"瀨屎屁"},{"pid":"bc2f24605e62e6b349869c933d0d578c67e79106","tid":1894997,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b808332d9af0c58e7ae9059f260b363595f9c979","tid":1894997,"uid":290620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"要除褲放屁 💨💨💨"}]}